fettuccine (0.9.3) unstable; urgency=low
  * A widget overlay interface has been added, with a few basic controls.  These controls can be enabled or hidden from the widget options dialog box.
  * A more complete default list of webcams now ships with the app.  Also, you can now reset back to this list from the "Import Webcam List" dialog box.
  * Authentication support has been improved slightly, with the option now to continue loading a webcam despite SSL errors.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Sat, 19 Jul 2014 13:39:59 -0400

fettuccine (0.9.2) unstable; urgency=low
  * Basic authentication now supported, for webcams that require a username and password.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Wed, 09 Jul 2014 23:19:24 -0400

fettuccine (0.9.1) unstable; urgency=low
  * Fettuccine now stops downloading new images when the screen is dark.  (Thanks Sixwheeledbeast!)
  * Fettuccine now stops constantly asking for a new network connection if the current connection goes down.  (Thanks Xes!)
  * Widget settings dialog cleaned up a bit.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Tue, 08 Jul 2014 22:29:56 -0400

fettuccine (0.9.0) unstable; urgency=low
  * Running Fettuccine as a desktop widget is now supported.

